# stow tree-folds ~/.local/bin into this directory, so anything installed into
# ~/.local/bin (uv, uvx, `uv tool install` shims like devbox-*, etc.) lands
# here and would otherwise show up as dirty. Blanket-ignore everything and only
# track the hand-maintained scripts below.
*
!.gitignore
!cb
!cs
!oc
!qm
